 P2y.jp  https://p2y.jp 2023 年 7 月 20 日星期四 09:11:35 +0000 zh每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.2.2 https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cropped-logo_2023_150x150-32x32.png P2y.jp https://p2y.jp 32 32 166157578
 VTuber Suisei Hoshimachi 将亮相 2023 年阿苏摇滚音乐节 Hololive 首次户外音乐节亮相https://p2y.jp/vtuber-hoshimachi-suisei-to-perform-at-aso-rock-festival-2023-first-outdoor-fes-appearance-by-hololive-talents/ https://p2y.jp/vtuber-hoshimachi-suisei-to-perform-at-aso-rock-festival-2023-first-outdoor-fes-appearance-by-hololive-talents/#respondp2y_admin Thu, 20 Jul 2023 08:26:58 +0000 VTuberバーチャル音楽ASO ROCK FESTIVAL(阿蘇ロックフェスティバル)YouTuberバーチャルYouTuberバーチャルアイドルバーチャルシンガーホロライブホロライブプロダクション南阿蘇村星街すいせい熊本県野外フェス https://p2y.jp/?p=96890 <p>阿苏摇滚音乐节秘书处将于2023年7月20日、9月30日至10月1日（令和5年）举办户外音乐节“ASO ROCK FESTIVAL FIRE 2023”。</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-hoshimachi-suisei-to-perform-at-aso-rock-festival-2023-first-outdoor-fes-appearance-by-hololive-talents/">VTuber Suisei Hoshimachi 亮相 2023 年阿苏摇滚音乐节 Hololive 首次户外音乐节首次出现</a>在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>阿苏摇滚音乐节事务局将参加预定于2023年7月20日、9月30日至10月1日举办的户外音乐节“ <strong>ASO ROCK FESTIVAL FIRE 2023</strong> ”。据宣布，VTuber <strong>Suisei Hoshimachi</strong> （所属：Hololive）将出现。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="96894" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-hoshimachi-suisei-to-perform-at-aso-rock-festival-2023-first-outdoor-fes-appearance-by-hololive-talents/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,677" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" decoding="async" width="1200" height="677" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/vtuber_hoshimachi_suisei_to_perform_at_aso_rock_festival_2023_first_outdoor_fes_appearance_by_hololive_talents.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-96894"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：推特<br>© 2023 年阿苏摇滚音乐节火。<br> © 2016 COVER 公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>星町水成将成为第一个出现在 VTuber 办公室 Hololive Production 旗下日本女子组合“Holo Live”户外音乐节的艺人。</p><p> “ASO ROCK FESTIVAL FIRE 2023”是在熊本县南阿苏村的熊本露天剧场 Aspecta 举办的户外摇滚音乐节。 Suisei Hoshimachi预计将于9月30日亮相，Ulfuls、Kyary Pamyu Pamyu、小泉恭子、Sambomaster等其他著名艺人也预定亮相。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/suisei_hosimati/status/1681939231969775618" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc9WCNtgOJKCG6m7ZJJPVxl0hzierAmzlAJW-zpK-lGSmwR8bIVNR7xaNmAeW3s5EXMSpJfORgErlDjiV6uCEEIFZCFLuXDe8Ef4Ftey_HkYt5XqN-M1OAdx4cuNgOddD-D3JvmUahe9w5YtRIO7PE4L=w1097-h806-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><div class="uajoo64b92867edea8" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
