</style><h3 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">来自 Cover Co., Ltd. 总裁 谷乡元明 (Motoaki Tanigo)</h3><p> <em>Cover Co., Ltd. 是一家致力于将日本尖端娱乐文化传播到世界各地的公司。这次，我们很高兴在我们运营的Hololive Production旗下的艺人粉丝交流活动“hololive Meet”中得到了同一虚拟领域公司VRChat的支持。</em> </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="QNOKxPRe2x"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-meet-announces-first-pop-up-store-in-taipei-taiwan/">Hololive Meet 首家快闪店已确定在台湾台北开业</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“hololive Meet 决定在台湾台北开设第一家快闪店” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-meet-announces-first-pop-up-store-in-taipei-taiwan/embed/#?secret=xIK9NXAJEV#?secret=QNOKxPRe2x" data-secret="QNOKxPRe2x" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000969.000030268.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="VRChat决定赞助VTuber办公室“Holo Live Production”和全球活动策划“hololive Meet”项目！">VRChat决定赞助VTuber办公室“Holo Live Production”和全球活动策划“hololive Meet”项目！</a></p><cite>公关时报</cite></blockquote><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p><a href="https://hololivepro.com/news/20230719-01-47/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="VRChat决定赞助全球活动策划“hololive Meet”项目！">VRChat决定赞助全球活动策划“hololive Meet”项目！</a></p><p> <a href="https://hololivemeet.hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">hololive 相约</a></p><cite>全息直播制作</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="l1Tzlve55G"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vrchat-sponsored-hololive-meet-an-international-event-project-by