-raising-suspicions-she-has-in-the-past-made-statements-referring-to-former-professional-baseball-player/">VTuber 郡道美玲「野球のルールに疎い」に疑いの見方 過去に元プロ野球選手に言及する発言も</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber 郡道美玲「野球のルールに疎い」に疑いの見方 過去に元プロ野球選手に言及する発言も&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-gundo-mirei-unfamiliarity-with-baseball-rules-attitude-is-raising-suspicions-she-has-in-the-past-made-statements-referring-to-former-professional-baseball-player/embed/#?secret=Koy4dmA9aK#?secret=zaRhDYjFnn" data-secret="zaRhDYjFnn" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>更に、郡道さんが自身のメンバー限定配信内で、所謂「青い鯨」行為を行っていた疑いがあるとする情報も拡散しておりました。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="g2VMwAeo91"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-have-published-the-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-also-spreading-on-sns/">一部まとめサイト VTuber 郡道美玲の「青い鯨」行為疑惑を掲載 SNS上でも拡散か</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;一部まとめサイト VTuber 郡道美玲の「青い鯨」行為疑惑を掲載 SNS上でも拡散か&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/some-roundup-blogs-have-published-the-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-of-vtuber-gundo-mirei-also-spreading-on-sns/embed/#?secret=k3mQ5ltRf6#?secret=g2VMwAeo91" data-secret="g2VMwAeo91" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="M1NlCj4Afh"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/some-news-media-report-on-nijisanji-vtuber-gundo-mireis-alleged-blue-whale-challenge-this-appears-to-have-appeared-in-